N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 8 ยง 341.13 - Terms of office

State Regulations

Officers shall hold office for one year or until their
successors are installed. This one-year term shall be from June 1st of the
election year to May 31st of the following year. Officers may serve no more
than two terms per each office contingent upon the person's continued
eligibility to serve as a member of the student assembly. Notes
